rows.label: qst200502_0010
rows.name:
Meleph, I'm sorry, but could
you help in the kitchen?

rows.label: qst200502_0020
rows.name: What? You want me to help?

rows.label: qst200502_0030
rows.name:
Meleph is suited for tasks that
require care and elegance.

rows.label: qst200502_0040
rows.name:
I see. I don't quite understand,
but I will lend my full support.

rows.label: qst200502_0050
rows.name:
Tora and Hana, could I ask you
to restock the ingredients?

rows.label: qst200502_0070
rows.name: What and how many do you need, mo?

rows.label: qst200502_0100
rows.name:
Got it, mo. We'll bring
a suitable amount, mo.

rows.label: qst200502_0110
rows.name:
Byakko, I'd like to ask
you to go shopping.

rows.label: qst200502_0120
rows.name: Of course. I shall go at once.

rows.label: qst200502_0130
rows.name:
The rest of you, please
attract customers.

rows.label: qst200502_0150
rows.name:
It's probably the first shop in Alst's
history with sweets handmade by a Blade!

rows.label: qst200502_0160
rows.name:
They're the most delicious, so
everyone please come and try them!
